{
  "stem": "5471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were hiding, so they had been against the Germans, and they were put in separate barracks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not allowed to walk free through the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, I think, we're not allowed to have [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] visitors from outside the-- of other people from the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were punished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mainly keeping contact between people in the camp and outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they needed something from outside, I went on my bike to Assen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from there on, they try to get papers in, what they needed or give a message through, what was needed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What they called career jobs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to Assen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was about 14 kilometers from the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I always did that on my bike.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hmm, the back wheel was all right, but front wheel had a rubber strip.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very hard, so I had several falls with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when there's a pebble in front of it and the wheel touches it, It turns over and you fall.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how I made it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was pregnant, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was going to be our peace child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was born in July '45.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, when the war ended, a lot of people came to me, kiss me, and said, now, we are going to have a child of peace, which was my son.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bring messages over from outside to another.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it all depended what was needed at that moment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes it could be something of sending close.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or it could be papers were to be editing or papers what was-- were needed to get out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was possible too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Several ways.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Could be for to see a specialist, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
